sed as a short form of   Nancy ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"When Anne Eaton was born about 1277, in Eaton, Cheshire, England, United Kingdom, her father, Richard Eaton, was 27 and her mother, Isabel, was 25. She had at least 1 son and 1 daughter with John Donne."},"et":{"abt1277–":"umbes 1277–Surnud","1277–Female":"1277–Surnud","1275–Male":"1275–Surnud","1300–Male":"1300–Surnud","1345–Female":"1345–Surnud","1252–1277":"1252–1277","1254–Female":"1254–Surnud","1345":"1345","abt1277":"umbes 1277","1300":"1300","1277":"1277","ABT 1300":"umbes 1300","1254":"1254","about 1345":"umbes 1345","1275":"1275","1252":"1252","Eaton, Ches, Eng":"Eaton, Cheshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Utkinton, Ches, Eng":"Utkinton, Cheshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"abt1277–":"noin 1277–Kuollut","1277–Female":"1277–Kuollut","1275–Male":"1275–Kuollut","1300–Male":"1300–Kuollut","1345–Female":"1345–Kuollut","1252–1277":"1252–1277","1254–Female":"1254–Kuollut","1345":"1345","abt1277":"noin 1277","1300":"1300","1277":"1277","ABT 1300":"noin 1300","1254":"1254","about 1345":"noin 1345","1275":"1275","1252":"1252","Eaton, Ches, Eng":"Eaton, Cheshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Utkinton, Ches, Eng":"Utkinton, Cheshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"abt1277–":"environ 1277–Décédée","1277–Female":"1277–Décédée","1275–Male":"1275–Décédé","1300–Male":"1300–Décédé","1345–Female":"1345–Décédée","1252–1277":"1252–1277","1254–Female":"1254–Décédée","1345":"1345","abt1277":"environ 1277","1300":"1300","1277":"1277","ABT 1300":"environ 1300","1254":"1254","about 1345":"environ 1345","1275":"1275","1252":"1252","Eaton, Ches, Eng":"Eaton, Cheshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Utkinton, Ches, Eng":"Utkinton, Cheshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Lorsque Anne Eaton est née environ 1277, à Eaton, Cheshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, son père, Richard Eaton, avait 27 ans et sa mère, Isabel, avait 25 ans. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils et 1 fille avec John Donne."},"de":{"abt1277–":"u